snippet.title: Childhood Friendship - Doki Doki Blue Skies Teaser #2 (Sayori's Route)
snippet.description:
Ever wondered how MC and Sayori first met? This little snippet from Sayori’s route will show you how. Sayori hasn’t changed all too much, has she?

There are a few other flashbacks which you’ll see at full release!
